cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS 

The paper deals with the challenge of balancing privacy and explainability in machine learning models, which is a common problem in the field of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the issue of privacy in the context of differential privacy (cs.CR) and proposes a family of simple models for approximating complex models (cs.AI). The experiments conducted in the paper involve image benchmark datasets (cs.CV) and a medical dataset (cs.DS).
